SELECT
    MAX_SID,
    src_sys_cd,
    agrmt_cd,
    agrmt_desc,
    agrmt_status,
    effective_date,
    expired_date,
    close_cmi,
    fleet_ctr
FROM
    (   SELECT
            lkp_tgt.MAX_SID,
            src.src_sys_cd,
            src.agrmt_cd,
            src.agrmt_desc,
            src.agrmt_status,
            src.effective_date,
            src.expired_date,
            src.close_cmi,
            src.fleet_ctr
        FROM
            (   SELECT
                    DISTINCT CAST('axis' AS VARCHAR(6))   AS src_sys_cd , 
                    CAST(cagrseg AS         VARCHAR(10))  AS agrmt_cd , 
                    CAST(tagrseg AS         VARCHAR(200)) AS agrmt_desc , 
                    CAST(estado AS          VARCHAR(10))  AS agrmt_status , 
                    CAST(fec_crea AS        TIMESTAMP)    AS effective_date , 
                    CAST(fec_mod AS         TIMESTAMP)    AS expired_date , 
                    CAST(cierracmi AS       INTEGER)      AS close_cmi , 
                    CAST(cflota AS          INTEGER)      AS fleet_ctr , 
                    1                                     AS DUMMY
                FROM 
                    (   SELECT 
                            *, 
                            ROW_NUMBER() over ( PARTITION BY 
                                               cagrseg, 
                                               cidioma 
                                           ORDER BY 
                                               rec_crt_dtm DESC, 
                                               seq_id DESC) RN 
                        FROM
                            cdp_stg_dwh.sisaxis_ctr_desagrupaseg)driver
                WHERE 
                    cidioma=3 
                AND rn=1 )src
        LEFT JOIN 
            (   SELECT 
                    1                  AS DUMMY, 
                    MAX(dim_agrmt_key) AS MAX_SID 
                FROM 
                    cdp_dwh.dim_agreement_t) LKP_TGT
        ON 
            LKP_TGT.DUMMY=src.DUMMY )

select distinct dim_agrmt_key,
agrmt_cd,
src_sys_cd,
rec_crt_dtm
from
cdp_dwh.dim_agreement_t 
where 
src_sys_cd='axis'
